    <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4"><div class="pf-module-card"><span class="pf-status"><span class="pf-dot"></span> Planned</span><h2 class="pf-module-title"><a href="/internal/settings/business-profile">Business Profile</a></h2><p class="text-muted mb-0">Manage the Parfait business profile, Meta setup, analytics scope, and shared backend integration.</p></div></div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4"><div class="pf-module-card"><span class="pf-status"><span class="pf-dot"></span> Planned</span><h2 class="pf-module-title">Creative</h2><p class="text-muted mb-0">Review which images, videos, hooks, and offers drive shopping behavior.</p></div></div>
</section>
